title: Indestructible Hulk 012
description:
"AGENT OF T.I.M.E." PART 2! The team-up you've been waiting for: HULK and...BRUCE BANNER?In the last hours before the extinction of the dinosaurs, it's Hulk vs. the CHRONARCHISTS!And who is the true TOMORROW MAN?Guest starring KID COLT, TWO GUN KID and RAWHIDE KID!!!



Q-Is the Hulk still wearing the armor?
A-Yes

Q-Why?
A-Because it helps him travel through time.

Q-That's not the reason they told us he wears the armor
A-I know

Q-Is it still stupid?
A-Yes

Q-Then why are you still reading it?
A-I hoping and prying that one of these days I'll pick up Indestructible Hulk and I will find a mind blowing story as good as Planet Hulk and World War Hulk, the series that got me reading comics again.

Keep hoping....
